# ==========================================
# STRIPE (stripe.com)
# Jak nastavit:
#   1. Spusť: STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_... node scripts/stripe-setup.mjs
#   2. Zkopíruj price IDs z výstupu scriptu
#   3. Nastav webhook v Stripe Dashboard → Developers → Webhooks
#      URL: https://coworkingcz.vercel.app/api/stripe/webhook
#      Events: checkout.session.completed, invoice.payment_succeeded,
#              customer.subscription.deleted, invoice.payment_failed
# ==========================================
